       "description": "Build the My Week page per PRD §10 (My Week surface) and §13 FR-2.\n\n**MyWeekPage component:**\n- Displays current week plan or upcoming draft (auto-selects based on lifecycle stage).\n- Week selector to navigate between weeks.\n- Plan state badge (DRAFT, LOCKED, RECONCILING, RECONCILED) with compliance indicator.\n- Lock/Reconcile action buttons (contextual based on plan state).\n\n**CommitList component:**\n- Ordered list of commits showing: priority rank, chess piece icon, title, RCDO path, estimate points, linked ticket key, status.\n- Drag-and-drop reorder using a library (e.g., @dnd-kit/sortable). Keyboard-accessible reorder alternative: move-up/move-down buttons per commit (WCAG 2.1 AA).\n- Inline expand to show description, success criteria, provenance info if carried forward.\n- Edit and delete actions per commit (only in DRAFT state).\n\n**CommitForm component (modal or panel):**\n- Fields: title (required), description (textarea), chess piece (radio/select with piece icons and descriptions), estimate points (segmented control: 1/2/3/5/8), primary RCDO link (hierarchical selector using RcdoTreeView in picker mode), success criteria (textarea, required badge for King/Queen), linked ticket (search/select).\n- Real-time validation: required fields highlighted, chess piece limits checked (show 'Max 1 King already used' warning), RCDO linkage rules enforced.\n- Carry-forward provenance banner if commit was carried forward (shows source week and streak count).\n\n**CapacityMeter component:**\n- Visual bar/gauge showing committed points vs weekly budget (default 10).\n- Color-coded: green (under budget), yellow (near budget), red (over budget).\n- Breakdown by chess piece type.\n- Override indicator if manager has set custom capacity.\n\n**Soft warnings panel:**\n- Warning if >8 active commits in the plan.\n- Warning if >40% of total points are Pawn commits.\n- These are UI warnings only, not lock blockers.\n\n**Component tests:** commit list renders in priority order, drag-drop reorder updates priority, commit form validates all required fields, chess piece limit enforced in UI, capacity meter shows correct totals, soft warnings appear at thresholds, RCDO selector enforces linkage rules, keyboard reorder works.",
