       "description": "Build the lock and reconciliation flows per PRD §10, §11 (Flows 1-4), §13 FR-3/FR-5/FR-6.\n\n**Lock flow (within My Week page):**\n- Pre-lock validation panel: runs validation and displays results as two sections: Hard Errors (block lock) and Soft Warnings (informational). Hard errors: missing required fields, chess piece limit violations. Soft warnings: AI lint results (added in later step, placeholder panel here).\n- Lock confirmation dialog: shows summary of commits being locked, total points, RCDO coverage. Confirm/cancel buttons.\n- On lock success: show baseline captured confirmation, plan transitions to LOCKED state in UI.\n- Auto-lock status: if plan was auto-locked, show banner indicating system lock with any validation errors that existed.\n\n**Post-lock edit flow (within My Week page, LOCKED state):**\n- Edit/add/remove commit actions available but route through scope change dialog.\n- ScopeChangeDialog: requires reason category (from ScopeChangeCategory enum) and reason text. Shows before/after comparison for edits.\n- Change timeline view: chronological list of all scope changes since lock.\n\n**ReconcilePage component:**\n- Two-column comparison: baseline snapshot (left) vs current state (right) for each commit.\n- Per commit: baseline values (chess piece, estimate, RCDO, title) vs current values. Highlight changes in red/green.\n- Scope change summary section: list of all post-lock changes grouped by type.\n- Linked ticket evidence: for each commit with a linked ticket, show ticket current status and status history summary.\n- Outcome selector per commit: ACHIEVED (green), PARTIALLY_ACHIEVED (yellow), NOT_ACHIEVED (red), CANCELED (gray). Auto-populated to ACHIEVED if linked ticket is Done.\n- Reconcile notes: textarea per commit, required for PARTIALLY_ACHIEVED, NOT_ACHIEVED, CANCELED (validation enforced).\n- Carry-forward section: for NOT_ACHIEVED and PARTIALLY_ACHIEVED commits, offer carry-forward checkbox. CarryForwardDialog: select reason from controlled list, optional text, confirm target week.\n- Submit reconciliation button: validates all commits have outcomes and required notes. Shows confirmation summary.\n\n**Component tests:** pre-lock validation shows errors and warnings, lock blocked on hard errors, scope change dialog captures reason, reconcile view renders baseline vs actual, outcome selector works, required notes enforced, carry-forward dialog creates request, auto-achieve shown for Done tickets.",
