       "id": "step-18",
       "title": "Derived read models and operational reporting",
       "description": "Implement derived read models and reporting per PRD §21, §23.\n\n**Derived tables (Flyway migrations):**\n- `user_week_fact`: userId, weekStart, planState, lockCompliance, reconcileCompliance, totalPlannedPoints, totalAchievedPoints, commitCount, carryForwardCount, scopeChangeCount, kingCount, queenCount.\n- `team_week_rollup`: teamId, weekStart, memberCount, lockedCount, reconciledCount, totalPlannedPoints, totalAchievedPoints, exceptionCount, avgCarryForwardRate.\n- `rcdo_week_rollup`: rcdoNodeId, weekStart, plannedPoints, achievedPoints, commitCount, teamContributionBreakdown (JSON).\n- `compliance_fact`: userId, weekStart, lockOnTime, lockLate, autoLocked, reconcileOnTime, reconcileLate, reconcileMissed.\n- `carry_forward_fact`: commitId, sourceWeek, currentWeek, streakLength, rcdoNodeId, chessPiece.\n\n**Refresh service:**\n- `ReadModelRefreshService`: recomputes derived tables.\n- Event-driven refresh: triggered by lock, reconcile, scope change, carry-forward events.\n- Scheduled refresh: runs every 5 minutes for current-week data (fallback if events missed).\n- Idempotent: safe to re-run without creating duplicates.\n\n**Reporting API:**\n- `GET /api/reports/compliance?teamId=&weekStart=&weekEnd=` — lock/reconcile compliance by team/week.\n- `GET /api/reports/planned-vs-achieved?teamId=&weekStart=&weekEnd=` — points comparison.\n- `GET /api/reports/carry-forward?teamId=&weekStart=&weekEnd=` — carry-forward rates and streaks.\n- `GET /api/reports/chess-distribution?teamId=&weekStart=` — chess piece distribution.\n- `GET /api/reports/scope-changes?teamId=&weekStart=&weekEnd=` — scope change volume.\n- `GET /api/reports/rcdo-coverage?rcdoNodeId=&weekStart=&weekEnd=` — RCDO branch effort.\n- `GET /api/reports/ai-acceptance` — AI suggestion acceptance rates.\n- `GET /api/reports/exception-aging?teamId=` — unresolved exception age.\n- All reports query derived tables, not transactional tables (P95 < 1.5s target).\n\n**Manager dashboard optimization:**\n- Team Week dashboard components updated to query from derived read model endpoints instead of live aggregation.\n- Verify P95 dashboard query under 1.5 seconds.\n\n**Unit tests:** derived table refresh computes correct aggregates, idempotent re-runs produce same results, event-driven refresh triggered on lifecycle events, report endpoints return correctly filtered data, dashboard queries use read models.",
